  "detailed_description": "<h1>v1.1 The Remix Update</h1><p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>v1.1: The Remix Update is Available Now!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Go toe-to-toe with the RNG gods on Remix Island in our new randomizer mode with 4 huge stages. Find or choose from a dozen new upgrades and climb the difficulty ladder with the new Difficulty Shop.</p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In the quaint, happy world of Beeflandia - our hero, <strong>Beef Cat</strong>, and friends always found ways to celebrate good times. The vibes certainly changed, however, when <strong>Some Big Guy</strong> showed up and started causing a ruckus.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2796510/extras/4732072a23cf7edacddac4d8b876c98d.poster.avif?t=1735232741\" width=612 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2796510/extras/4732072a23cf7edacddac4d8b876c98d.webm?t=1735232741\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2796510/extras/4732072a23cf7edacddac4d8b876c98d.mp4?t=1735232741\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2796510/extras/efd14c04774d1ffeaac63dbff64db780.webp?t=1735232741\" width=341 height=22 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Several</strong> Visually Distinct Worlds</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >7+ Game Modes (Survivors/Gauntlet/Collectathon)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>6</strong> Playable Characters</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Dozens</strong> of Unique Pickups</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Fully Original</strong> Chiptune Rock Soundtrack</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2796510/extras/ec672b8a5a96e33e9534ce875bdbf61f.poster.avif?t=1735232741\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2796510/extras/ec672b8a5a96e33e9534ce875bdbf61f.webm?t=1735232741\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2796510/extras/ec672b8a5a96e33e9534ce875bdbf61f.mp4?t=1735232741\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2796510/extras/9d063a6cbcc6d5736e9c8341131b0da7.webp?t=1735232741\" width=409 height=22 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Beeflandia always finds ways to change the game, so <strong>be prepared to adapt on the fly.</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Survivors</strong> has you scrambling through hand-crafted stages collecting items and beating baddies for a certain time limit. Recognizable and classic Survivors gameplay</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>Gauntlet</strong> has you exploring linear stages destroying enemy spawners while you collect keys and unlock gates like the classic Gauntlet series. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>Collectathon</strong> has you exploring set piece focused stages in the hunt to find all the collectible gemmies</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>Horde</strong> has you in a tight arena with a regular timed interval of upgrades and tasks you with defeating a certain number of a specific enemy </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>Boss</strong> stages put you against large multi-attack based boss foes in tight arenas with a limited toolkit</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Volleyball and Deathmatch</strong> pit you in tight competitive arenas against either AI opponents or another real player via shared screen local play or Steam Remote Play</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2796510/extras/5f125b613d94467aa804728acb90829e.poster.avif?t=1735232741\" width=638 height=358 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2796510/extras/5f125b613d94467aa804728acb90829e.webm?t=1735232741\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2796510/extras/5f125b613d94467aa804728acb90829e.mp4?t=1735232741\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2796510/extras/e9f213b3b8a0245b15845f0d411dad17.webp?t=1735232741\" width=308 height=23 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Navigate a retro over-world map</strong> as you clear stages in a somewhat loose order that allows you to pick and choose your favorite game modes.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find tents in the world map to <strong>unlock new playable characters</strong> that have distinct play styles ranging from completely defensive kits to kits focused on speed and critical hits.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use the coins you collect in stages at shops to <strong>buy permanent stat boosts or unlock shortcuts</strong> and more.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2796510/extras/af9ca4cbb8d046e3e3ecd48564702442.avif?t=1735232741\" width=673 height=108 /></span></p>",
